## 9. Oral defense (short)

- **Bug:** unbounded effect of **`fgets`** into an undersized stack buffer for the password line.
- **Why login is a red herring:** no **`system`** in the binary; **`admin`** validates in **`verify_user_pass`** but **`main`** still branches to the failure **`puts`** on **`eax == 0`**, and ‚Äúsuccess‚Äù would only **`return 0`** anyway.
- **Fix:** use **`fgets`** with **`sizeof(buf)-1`**, ensure **`sizeof(buf)`** matches allocation, stack canaries, **PIE/NX** as appropriate, or **`read`** with explicit length checks.
